<|channel>thought
<channel|># 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或生意虧損時，決定賣出資產以防止損失進一步擴大（即係「止損」）。
eng:cut losses / stop loss
<eg>
yue:個股票跌得太勁，我決定止蝕，唔想再蝕更多錢。 (go3 gu2 piu2 dit3 dak1 tai3 ging6, ngo5 kyut3 ding6 zi2 sik1, m4 soeng2 zoi3 sik1 gang3 do1 cin2.)
eng:The stock price has dropped too sharply, so I decided to cut my losses to avoid losing more money. [end of text]


